Interface BacktrackHomomorphism.Scheduler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BCCScheduler
    Enclosing class:
    BacktrackHomomorphism

    public static interface BacktrackHomomorphism.Scheduler
    The Scheduler interface provides a way to manage the backtracking order. The Var.previousLevel will be used when the backtracking algorithm is in a failure state (allow backjumping).
